    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! It truly breaks my heart to let this absolute beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy the ride of their life. This car has been my absolute pride and joy\u2014always garage-kept, hand-washed every single Sunday, and treated like royalty. Honestly, it still has that fresh feeling as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. There might be a tiny, microscopic mark somewhere if you really go looking with a spotlight, but to the naked eye, she\u2019s just stunning. You won\u2019t find another one this clean in the neighborhood. Come by, have a coffee, and see for yourself\u2014you're going to fall in love!",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
